PCase72.hs:(17,15)-(20,9): Splicing expression
    ghc-internal:GHC.Internal.TH.Quote.quoteExp
      pCase
      " s of\n\
      \         \"hello\" -> s .== s =: qed\n\
      \         _       -> s .== s =: qed\n\
      \       "
  ======>
    cases
      [((.==) s (literal "hello") ==> (s .== s =: qed)),
       (sNot ((.==) s (literal "hello")) ==> (s .== s =: qed))]
